sentences: Anna Lovisa Johnsson (Jonsson), better known by her stage name Ana Johnsson (Swedish pronunciation: [ˈǎnːa ˈjǔːnsɔn]; born October 4, 1977), is a Swedish singer and songwriter, best known for the song "We Are" from the Spider-Man 2 soundtrack.
Her debut album, Cuz I Can, was released in April 2004 in Sweden, followed several months later by an international release under the name The Way I Am, containing several new songs.
Her second album, Little Angel, was released in October 2006.

Johnsson's second album Little Angel was released in Sweden on October 18, 2006.
The song was used as the title song of the Finnish-Chinese movie Jadesoturi (Jade Warrior), and appeared on its soundtrack, which was released on October 11, 2006, in Finland.

Plans for going back into the studio to record a new album during the fall of 2012 were dismissed due to personal life reasons, after which her musical career has been put on hold.
